welcome to gallery search using flickr application
 steps to start this application

 step1:install python3 using sudo apt-get install python3
 step2:create virtualenv for starting application
      pip3 install virtualenv
      virtualenv -p python3 env
      python3 -m venv my_env
 step3:Install pip3
 step4:run to install modules (pip3 install -r ./requirements.txt), this file will install all required modules
       for application
 step5:Set development environment for application using `export FLASK_ENV=development`
 step6 after followed all step mentioned above please go to the application dir and run ./server.sh
 step7:Go to browser and hit "http://127.0.0.1:5000/" will redirect you on search bar and type anythings in search
       and click on search button, it will redirect you on result page where you will see all images


Suggestion for prod deployment
--->>>>Web Server Gateway Interface (WSGI) HTTP server compatible with various web frameworks, including Flask

1. change all config file like db connection , secret key redis email smtp etc.
2. write script to install all dependencies for project like modules
3. set env to prod before deployment
4. all test cases should be there after and move application to maintaince mode and start all test cases
5. give the required permission to all files
6. for email sent purpose there must be a business account
7. use CI/CD to deployment


Note: before deployement to prod there should be pre prod it will be to test all cases


